{"tid":802282,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"主人餵素食給雪橇犬　到底牠愛吃素還是肉？","createTime":"2018-09-01T11:02:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-01T14:28:05.000Z","uid":32938,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f4b71c27cc103eadc528e93b2dd4e570c1181121","tid":802282,"uid":32938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T11:02:19.000Z","msg":"英國節目This Morning日前請來一位非素食者的主人和她的素食狗狗，並在狗狗面前放了一碗肉和一碗蔬菜，讓狗狗選擇吃哪一碗，看看到底狗狗愛吃素還是肉？<br />\n<br />\n該名被請來的主人並非一位素食者，她指會餵素食給狗狗，是因為發現了狗狗在夏天時吃特別少肉，而她又擔心狗狗會因此吃不飽，於是她在今年夏天開始餵素食給她的雪橇犬，不過，狗狗就似乎未如她想像般愛吃蔬菜。<br />\n<br />\n在節目中，工作人員將一碗肉和一碗蔬菜放在狗狗面前，而狗狗當下毫不猶疑地走向了那碗肉，聞了兩下就狼吞虎嚥起來，雖然途中有停下來聞了聞另一碗蔬菜，但聞完後也就回頭繼續吃那碗肉。由此可見，狗狗對肉的喜愛遠大於蔬菜。<br />\n<br />\n主人看到後就表示：「我沒有保證過牠一定會吃甚麼，而公平地說，現在的氣溫下降了不少。」她亦指當初狗狗對於吃素表現得很開心，好像很樂於接受素食。<br />\n<br />\n不過她也未曾想過要之後要一直餵素食給狗狗，並謂：「我不想將素食強加於任何人，因為我父母也是素食者，我們討論過很多次這話題。」現在她承諾會再次餵肉給狗狗吃，她說：「如果這是她想要的，我會相應地進行調整。」<br />\n<br />\n不少觀眾看過節目後，都批評該名主人改變了狗狗的飲食習慣，剝奪了讓狗狗選擇的權利，有網民直指「狗是肉食動物！這是虐待動物！」，亦有網民批評該主人「這是甚麼粗心蠢主人！」<br />\n<br />\n對此，有獸醫表示狗是雜食動物，讓狗狗吃素是剝奪了牠們遵從天性吃肉的需要，並謂：「歷史演變決定了狗需要吃肉和蔬菜，以取得足夠礦物質和維生素。」而狗狗透過吃肉能獲得的氨基酸和維生素D等物質，都是必須依賴進食來攝取的物質。"},{"pid":"9a909a030c82a25b9fbf73f64210387c5f985fec","tid":802282,"uid":1348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T11:04:00.000Z","msg":"上帝創造了食物鏈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ad9f4c607f9f5999191c55efb0f2603b50c2442","tid":802282,"uid":1348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T11:04:24.000Z","msg":"唔食肉即係違反上帝既定律"},{"pid":"cc6ea33227e68ea8d136df4abb215becd3eb6463","tid":802282,"uid":180913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T11:06:13.000Z","msg":"其實素食狗好危險"},{"pid":"334f2faf8210f2cb99c66f84dd7f723a55404b5d","tid":802282,"uid":59014,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T11:07:39.000Z","msg":"最好食撚埋個主人"},{"pid":"0750ab9e35f8bfc50b7651571cebe1e788dd6060","tid":802282,"uid":120715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc6ea33227e68ea8d136df4abb215becd3eb6463","tid":802282,"uid":180913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T11:06:13.000Z","msg":"其實素食狗好危險"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T11:14:25.000Z","msg":"最好唔好係佢面前流血"},{"pid":"0f5ef2335dd379a0258a64bc6b37c875ab6a6df9","tid":802282,"uid":135866,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T11:24:02.000Z","msg":"世上3大煩膠<br />\nvegetarianism feminism Environmentalism"},{"pid":"1b4a9365f7930cdd724268039a5be74dc03ffa07","tid":802282,"uid":1402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T11:49:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ohw.ooo/husky/huskybeg_connect.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fohw.ooo%2Fhusky%2Fhuskybeg_connect.gif&h=fe01b70b&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ohw.ooo/husky/huskybeg_connect.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fohw.ooo%2Fhusky%2Fhuskybeg_connect.gif&h=fe01b70b&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ohw.ooo/husky/huskybeg_connect.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fohw.ooo%2Fhusky%2Fhuskybeg_connect.gif&h=fe01b70b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"015257fb96ff9003b55fd752b5fcad99e1c298fb","tid":802282,"uid":35585,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T11:51:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.imgur.com/MW5HhoF.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FMW5HhoF.gif&h=a34be26b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6dbfde0a872740defcca1fe583f05705530a4d72","tid":802282,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T11:53:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://ohw.ooo/husky/huskybeg_connect.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fohw.ooo%2Fhusky%2Fhuskybeg_connect.gif&h=fe01b70b&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ohw.ooo/husky/huskybeg_connect.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"h